msgctxt "sn25.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 25 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 25 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn25.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Cakkhuvagga "
msgstr "1. The Eye "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Rūpataṇhāsutta → taṇhāsuttaṃ (bj) | taṇhā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn25.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Rūpataṇhāsutta "
msgstr "8. Craving For Sights "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn25.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn25.8:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpataṇhā, bhikkhave, aniccā vipariṇāmī aññathābhāvī; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, craving for sights is impermanent, perishing, and changing. "

msgctxt "sn25.8:1.3"
msgid "saddataṇhā … "
msgstr "Craving for sounds, "

msgctxt "sn25.8:1.4"
msgid "gandhataṇhā … "
msgstr "craving for smells, "

msgctxt "sn25.8:1.5"
msgid "rasataṇhā … "
msgstr "craving for tastes, "

msgctxt "sn25.8:1.6"
msgid "phoṭṭhabbataṇhā … "
msgstr "craving for touches, "

msgctxt "sn25.8:1.7"
msgid "dhammataṇhā aniccā vipariṇāmī aññathābhāvī. "
msgstr "and craving for thoughts are impermanent, perishing, and changing. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn25.8:1.8"
msgid "Yo, bhikkhave, ime dhamme evaṃ saddahati adhimuccati, ayaṃ vuccati ‘saddhānusārī … pe … "
msgstr "Someone who has faith and confidence in these principles is called a follower by faith. …” "

msgctxt "sn25.8:1.9"
msgid "sambodhiparāyano’”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn25.8:1.10"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
